item.title: About me
item.description: Hello, I’m a junior data scientist with main interest in evaluating and creating data-driven business decisions by applying various data science skills. Now I am studying economics and statitstic in the university of nottingham(Ningbo). During my time at school, I finished courses including probability, statistic methods,regression modelling, and though it, developed expertise in formulating and implementing statistical approaches to pratical problems in business areas. Apart from learning from class, I also complete my toolbox by enrolling online courses (Datacamp, Coursera) related to python, machine learning and other real-world, data-focused skills.
